{"tid":549448,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《監獄風雲》真實版！東頭懲教所囚犯集體罷食　懲教署增援","createTime":"2018-02-03T15:31:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T17:23:59.000Z","uid":20933,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c7c183079b19c7d64a6f46c11be58d178ecb3dac","tid":549448,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:31:08.000Z","msg":"《監獄風雲》囚犯罷食情節在現實中上演！東頭懲教所一批囚犯在飯堂內發起罷食。懲教署稱據情報顯示，事件是因個別在囚人士因較早時被紀律檢控煽動其他在囚人士進行「集體非法活動」企圖對抗管方。<br />\n<br />\n事發在今日中午12時30分，懲教署指有17名外籍人士在東頭懲教所飯堂內罷食。署方即日調派區域應變隊及其他增援人員到頭懲教所，對目標地點及人物進行搜查，並指事件是由兩名外籍在囚人士懷疑煽動其他在囚人士參與集體非法活動，二人正被隔離及接受調查。署方稱，現時東頭懲教所情況穩定，署方會繼續密切監察有關情況和相關在囚人士的活動。<br />\n<br />\n東頭懲教所是本港一所低度設防監獄，專門羈押男性成年在囚人士。"},{"pid":"f1385ddbf132404b0f29ce71f279137a1d5ee297","tid":549448,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:31:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180203/57790017\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F57790017&d=z8jBNQZosMeRET1HuIIOQtZqoKrPvqrE%2FsQ53lv%2BkYo%3D&h=db1383f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180203%2F57790017&h=ecf8eb42\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180203/57790017</a>"},{"pid":"21976592ba01371c3664152beb106178a2adad6c","tid":549448,"uid":5503,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:51:31.000Z","msg":"因為我想你連屎都無得食啊"},{"pid":"307a609d9e22a22f3dc1e401b161bbdfd5410bd8","tid":549448,"uid":36543,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T15:56:02.000Z","msg":"絕食係示威定示弱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51a23a9399e8fd55cdcd06c646becd8327dc3c57","tid":549448,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"307a609d9e22a22f3dc